de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.heap

Class DoublePriorityObject<O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.heap.DoublePriorityObject<O>
  • Type Parameters:
    O - Stored object type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    PairInterface<Double,O>, Comparable<DoublePriorityObject<?>>

    public class DoublePriorityObject<O>
extends Object
implements PairInterface<Double,O>, Comparable<DoublePriorityObject<?>>
    Object for a priority queue with integer priority. Can be used in the UpdatableHeap, since hashcode and equality use the stored objects only, not the priority.
